<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Please correct me if I am wrong, but was NB's first Cursed kill not more than a couple months ago?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
