<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Yet you have been on G/E since at least September, which is as far back as our Rotation site goes apparently. For a guild who spent at least a couple months on just the GLYPHED/EXILED rotation, you guys are quick to forget your past and package it all into one big threesome kill.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
