No, we don't forget that we were on G/E rotation for a few months, but we were only on that rotation to get to Cursed.  If Glyphed, Exiled and Cursed spawned in three different locations in Ssra, we would never touch Glyphed, and be close to autopassing on Exiled.  I didn't package the three together, SOE did.  You can't get to Cursed, except via killing Glyphed/Exiled.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>At best you attempted Cursed every time you did the cycle and lost, which would still be &quot;blowing&quot; the spawn. Which is also a misnomer because you can get to the cursed spawn just find after killing the pseudo glyph/exiled replacements.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
